391
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:14,980
What medication did he give you that you'd treat me this way?

392
00:33:16,590 --> 00:33:18,870
Treat you this way?

393
00:33:20,290 --> 00:33:24,790
Every day I smile and look only at you.

394
00:33:25,460 --> 00:33:28,940
But you just play around with my mind every day, is this what you wanted?

395
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:33,510
Shangguan Qiu Yue, what you want is someone you can control

396
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:37,140
