399
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:55,510
Silly Sister, you have been manipulated by him.

400
00:33:55,510 --> 00:33:58,020
Qin Liufeng is from Fengming Mountain.

401
00:33:58,020 --> 00:34:00,940
He certainly has a lot of resentment toward me.

402
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:05,280
Big Brother, you sure are confident.

403
00:34:06,570 --> 00:34:08,770
It's Xiao Bai.

404
00:34:08,770 --> 00:34:11,170
Xiao Bai still misses you.

405
00:34:11,170 --> 00:34:15,310
So he used such a low tactic to come between us.

406
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:18,970
He doesn't have any tolerance,

407
00:34:18,970 --> 00:34:23,280
