408
00:34:25,290 --> 00:34:28,220
So are the tactics you used any better?

409
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:32,850
I am not like him.

410
00:34:32,850 --> 00:34:37,730
I just want to be good to you and Xiao Bai will only hurt you.

411
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:41,380
Brother, even at a time like this,

412
00:34:41,380 --> 00:34:44,810
